Business Rules:
BR1: Events must have a unique name within the same city.
BR2: Events must be associated with a city and a tour.
BR3: Events must not overlap in time if they are part of the same tour.
System Requirements:
SYSREQ1: Add a composite unique constraint on name and city_id in the Event table.
SYSREQ2: Establish foreign key relationships to link events with cities and tours.
SYSREQ3: Implement a time conflict validation in the service layer to ensure events in the same tour do not overlap.